This directory contains the Perseus text files for the Greek and Latin languages. To quote the project itself:

    Text Files - These are the original XML text files. 
    Download these files if you are generating the data 
    for the hopper yourself. Texts are licensed under 
    the Creative Commons ShareAlike 3.0 License[1]

The files are available from Perseus, too, for direct download.[2]

A copy of the Creative Commons ShareAlike 3.0 License is included within this file. All derivative works must be redistributed in accordance with this license.

[1] http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/opensource/download

[2] http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/opensource/downloads/texts/hopper-texts-GreekRoman.tar.gz
